{"tid":2120176,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[BNO] 提早提取強積金","createTime":"2020-07-22T13:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T00:48:09.000Z","uid":13915,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"cefbd43fb31b00b0f2d1ff362b3cb0da1dc61ba4","tid":2120176,"uid":13915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"(2) 永久性地離開香港：你必須聲明已經或將會離開香港，往其他地方居住，而無意作為永久性居民返回香港工作或再定居;並提供令受託人信納你已獲准在香港以外某地方居住的證明。<br />\n<br />\n注意： 假如計劃成員曾以此理由提早提取強積金，日後將不能以較後離港日期再次提出申請，受託人亦不會向計劃成員支付強積金。積金局備有曾以永久離港為理由而成功提取強積金的計劃成員紀錄冊。計劃成員如向受託人作出虛假或具誤導性的陳述，藉此提早提取強積金，可被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/main/employee/early_withdrawal_of_benefits.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Fmain%2Femployee%2Fearly_withdrawal_of_benefits.jsp&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgA4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=9e402e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/main/employee/early_withdrawal_of_benefits.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n如果要去英國既 記得拎埋MPF <br />\n唔知香港一下無晒大部份MPF會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfb7b74400990d2428c9173c1cdb5d14e918ab1","tid":2120176,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:39:53.000Z","msg":"全家拎曬啲MPF 走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf6b45d1517feba0fefd62517efa9c00dcde763","tid":2120176,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"離開香港必讀<p class=\"center\"></p>"},{"pid":"4e79163e3a51472d8907dd68d7fae8f89ebc51c4","tid":2120176,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"拎VISA都當係咩?"},{"pid":"0a9f3208d858b986c372ac7c45e7047ee124e782","tid":2120176,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:47:10.000Z","msg":"當然一個仙都唔可以留俾個垃圾政府"},{"pid":"6ca0af8b5b8413cf9407b9315265d06d00cd8785","tid":2120176,"uid":18